data.description: Priced to sell, this 3 BR, 1 1/2 BA, 1768 sq ft home is ready for its new owner to come in and put on the finishing touches. Bring your offer!! Excellent location on 1.06 acres in the country, it is conveniently just minutes away from US Highway 36 and 63. Master bedroom is located on the first floor. Large circular driveway for easy access and plenty of room for parking. Large 2 and 1/2 detached garage (24' x 36')  to park cars and storage with this private lot. This home also has a nice dry basement for dry food storage and a canning station. Come and check it out before it's gone!!
